author: kevan
msg: two very simply shell scripts that I use to help verify a release. getrelease.sh <artifact-url> will download the artifact, signature, sha1, and md5 checksums. verifyrelease.sh <artifact-filename> will verify the signature, and sha1 and md5 checksums. validation of these is via a neural network -- i.e. you eyeball the output
